# {{lb|en|idiomatic}} To feel [[irritable]]; to be in a bad [[mood]]; to have a bad [[day]] from the start, for no particular reason.
#: {{ux|en|I think my boss '''got up on the wrong side of the bed''' this morning. He's been grumpy all day.}}

